    "Name": "Hammerblow",
    "Details": "Clan Jade Falcon's brand new super heavy mech design, this mech is heavily armed but with a somewhat eclectic hardpoint mount setup for a superheavy, with no ballistic hardpoints in the torso. Designed with heavy combat in mind, the mech has plenty of free tonnage to use for heavy weaponry. The HBL-2 layout a pair of HAG 40s in the arms for massive damage, and matches them with twin Hyper Lasers sourced from the Republic Institute of Strategic Combat. The twin ER PPCs and SRM 6 launchers feel like afterthoughts compared to all the unusual weaponry.<br><br>S-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that substantially improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
